{"tid":2238584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警四度避答派員登機監視快艇","createTime":"2020-10-11T09:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T09:26:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9675693fb5d49fff3e7a9d0149f771c2cea34a95","tid":2238584,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/PF6D4TMAZJEFDAOQ2MUW3NY4BQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FPF6D4TMAZJEFDAOQ2MUW3NY4BQ%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=7c8ba8f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FPF6D4TMAZJEFDAOQ2MUW3NY4BQ%2F&h=7082a99c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/PF6D4TMAZJEFDAOQ2MUW3NY4BQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警四度避答派員登機監視快艇<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名港人疑偷渡往台灣途中被中國海警截獲，本報踢爆香港警方曾派員坐飛行服務隊定翼機高空監察12人出海過程，質疑一切盡在警方掌控之中，有設局送中之嫌。O記高級警司何振東昨拒正面回應有關指控是否屬實，更四度迴避記者提問，被質疑默認事件。<br />\n<br />\n何振東在記者會上四度被傳媒以廣東話及英文追問有關問題，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/irS6FqxFGK0Wn3NV_jQ2c0tZN-U=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QI6NEEW6IJGUFJJNEQHRYFKQEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FirS6FqxFGK0Wn3NV_jQ2c0tZN-U%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQI6NEEW6IJGUFJJNEQHRYFKQEY.jpg&h=4b81ef30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nO記高級警司何振東<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被質疑默認事件<br />\n<br />\n有記者指出，警方對於「警員曾坐飛行服務隊定翼機高空監察12人快艇」的報道一直不予置評，質疑警方是否形同默認有其事，而警方不否認有關指控，是否變相承認警方確有參與其中。何振東依然沒具體回應，並迴避正面回答問題，強調12名被捕人士全部有案在身，包括縱火、暴動、管有爆炸品以及勾結外國勢力等，全都是非常嚴重罪行。12人潛逃時被內地當局拘捕，何堅稱與香港警察無關。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。，懷疑有警員在機上於空中監察12港人乘坐的快艇。定翼機出動的時間及位置均與警方早前公佈12人登上快艇及駛離香港海域的資料脗合，警方疑一早知情。"},{"pid":"0851f7dd52c7979e6c397bdc06d30079d34a2f62","tid":2238584,"uid":264245,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"有問就岩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2487b93d9b1d807fa79039b6db1e5f6b80e3df","tid":2238584,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:10:07.000Z","msg":"何振東呢條仆街個眼神、態度好奸好串，睇記者會睇到眼火爆"},{"pid":"83f210aee2f0f2c3dc4a32b658e72667a0b7d677","tid":2238584,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"證據確鑿，不容置疑"},{"pid":"d552f2c5503ecb28750d16aacba07ba91c408312","tid":2238584,"uid":283428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e8b9e7eacc306f38209e430e88dd73f9723816","tid":2238584,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b2487b93d9b1d807fa79039b6db1e5f6b80e3df","tid":2238584,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:10:07.000Z","msg":"何振東呢條仆街個眼神、態度好奸好串，睇記者會睇到眼火爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"想車埋去"},{"pid":"5ce7a91ceaee8dd7cf3230942ce820623a1cdcf6","tid":2238584,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"}]}